{"tid":1251043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[下一步] 黃之鋒應該收拾心情，專心準備下星期既G20，去宣傳香港問題","createTime":"2019-06-22T10:42:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T13:26:29.000Z","uid":54684,"like":195,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"fbac155b876a8838e229eb76c419a555250e204c","tid":1251043,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T10:42:13.000Z","msg":"G20有幾重要，可以點宣揚香港人受欺壓，中港兩地點樣打壓港人，相信大家都明<br />\n全世界記者都會在場<br />\n其實都係時候諗下，有咩可以做<br />\n我覺得起碼有呢D︰<br />\n<br />\n- Make noise + 場外設booth放個Mon係度播compilation影片，不斷播放警察濫權片段，指出警察已違反邊一D國際公約<br />\n- 講醫院或有Backdoor問題，警察可以access政府醫療記錄，搜捕示威市民，已有5人被捕，叫大家小心華為<br />\n- 官員外國護照一覽，show清楚D，要求有關國家cut passports<br />\n- 總結︰簡單列出近年香港不斷遭壓迫之事<br />\n- 議員遭DQ<br />\n- 書商遭擄去<br />\n- 自己加<br />\n<br />\n云云組織之中，眾志仔應該算係最合適既，黃之鋒一出，全世界好多傳媒都會報。<br />\n個陣式可以係黃之鋒做英語宣傳，羅冠聰backup，周庭做日語宣傳。<br />\n大家點睇"},{"pid":"269e1ee5de288d28b9f4eb1e4a163140fe2f1f4f","tid":1251043,"uid":257330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T10:44:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"177f324391c81c9f5c07f51935c159115f1e98c7","tid":1251043,"uid":206021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T10:49:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"867b426a5c9ea2d53341de842adcef7d0fa94235","tid":1251043,"uid":199257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T10:52:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b5a90b7937f99408c4560e5100192b400c27907","tid":1251043,"uid":11254,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T10:52:41.000Z","msg":"周婷之鋒一齊啦 周又識日文"},{"pid":"9f3a9e10abcc1f89473e15637b811e6d10161c67","tid":1251043,"uid":94457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T10:52:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9fd288bfea411c7