6f.jpg&h=36d7e2c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58010a359c39bcb3419dfa6023353035de575b0e","tid":1251043,"uid":44174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T01:42:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"01890af982b7480bdec7ea2c15da2db92a7dab70","tid":1251043,"uid":251604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T01:45:13.000Z","msg":"Push one push"},{"pid":"666fb80ff3870dfe7ae89bb79155cbd6f10f0436","tid":1251043,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T02:05:54.000Z","msg":"黃之鋒 加 周庭 加 陳浩天"},{"pid":"bac475f6e652e20c0dd93261004054821e735ac6","tid":1251043,"uid":265467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T02:06:50.000Z","msg":"Sorry ，借位一用<br />\n<br />\n大家應該由問題根源去思考，與其一樣樣去反對政府D賣港政策，點解唔用真普選趕走曬班賣港賊，必須要令更多人知問題根源核心，個個支持真普選！！！<br />\n<br />\n現有大家要爭取D問題層次如果向上推，就會發現係香港現有制度出現問題，一日冇真普選，相同問題絕對會源源不絕！！！<br />\n<br />\n一日無真普選,建制派，港共政權賣港賊一車車補上，要徹底趕走賣港賊,只有真普選！！！各自跑山，真香港人加油！！<br />\n<br />\n［真普選救祖國行動］200年前香港割讓救國，如今中共有難，香港再割責無旁貸！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1252184\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1252184</a><br />\n<br />\n［請廣傳］香港只有真普選先可以趕走港共政府同建制派賣港賊！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1251736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1251736</a>"},{"pid":"1239217ea49180177d9d67584d1c72e6184b23dd","tid":1251043,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T02:09:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856fbe2d081712e6ffb6081ca77f265a7d200db0","tid":1251043,"uid":245813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T02:35:59.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n反正香港民間運動唔想要大台<br />\n而佢又算係喺香港嘅activists之中比較有國際知名度<br />\n呢個角色幾啱佢"},{"pid":"cdef00e5749f765ecda5459b5556243167cc123f","tid":1251043,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T02:43:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm